task.summary: Default task
Add a Marker in the map for each found place.
Add functional TODOs.
Format code.
Add action to take users to Wikipedia's pages when them tap on marker's title. Move Wikipedia objects to domain/wikipedia.
Add WikipediaService.java to put there the method to transform a page title into a URL.
Change search radius to 10km.
Change some messages to get user a better usage experience by giving him the same messages than Google Maps gives to them.
Add the first screenshot (from Google Maps with Wikipedia layer).
Display "Waiting for location" Toast when user has at least one location provider enabled.

Fix showing AlertDialog to enable providers when both providers are disabled while my app is not in the foreground. Take off the LocationManager parameter from methods to put it as a type's attribute.
Remove the second AlertDialog and change the negative button label to: "No, close app!" to simplify user life.
Refactor adding WikipediaDao.java and putting there the method to retrieve by REST the list of Wikipedia places.
Change application name to: "Tureame"
Add LegalNoticesActivity.java which will be displayed to the user when it access to the item "Legal notices" into the options menu from MapActivity.java.
Update Copyright adding 2013 year.
Change de List of providers for a Set.
Display a message to the users if there isn't any place to show to them.
Catch RestClientException to prevent showing an error to the user when having an IllegalArgumentException in Spring.
Create the LocationListener only once by setting it as a type attribute. Clear the map before adding new markers. Update minTime and minDistance for receive location updates.
